        <p class="text-base">We do not collect or store any personal data from our users. Any information provided to us is used solely for the purpose of responding to inquiries and providing support.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Cookie Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-base">Our website uses cookies to enhance your browsing experience. These cookies do not store any personal information and are used only to improve the functionality of the site.</p>
      </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
